  npcName: Young Girl
  dialogueLines:
  - Hiya! Did you know my daddy's the mayor?
  - Not a lot of people don't know it... but he's a big fat liar!
  - He said he'd get me a pet fishy soon- but I've been waiting soooooooooo long!
  - Will you go catch me one? Pretty please?
  - I want one of those silly orange ones!
  - Wow! It's even cuter than I immagined!
  - Thank you so much!!! Here you go!
  - Hopefully my daddy doesn't mind me giving that to you.
  - Hmmmm... What should I name you little fishy?
